                     <hi rend="largeCaps">GEORGE NOBLE</hi> (20)</persName>
                  <rs id="t18730609-400-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18730609-400-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18730609-400-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>, Stealing a purse, a pencil, a button, and 16<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 9<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. in money, from the person of <persName id="t18730609-name-115" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18730609-name-115" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18730609-name-115" type="surname" value="LOTT"></interp>
