                        <interp inst="t18730609-400-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. <hi rend="italic">He was further charged with having been convicted at Guildhall in March</hi>, 1872, <hi rend="italic">in the name of <persName id="t18730609-name-118">
                        <interp inst="t18730609-name-118" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
